---
title: User Registration Flow
author: Guy Schamp
---

@theme clean
@direction TB

#start User Visits Signup Page

  Enter Email & Password
  #decision Email Already Exists?
    -> yes: Show Error Message
    -> no: Create Account

  Show Error Message -> Enter Email & Password: "try again"

  Create Account
    Send Verification Email
    #delay Wait for Verification

  #decision Email Verified?
    -> yes: Activate Account
    -> no: #delay Wait for Verification: "resend"

  Activate Account
    Send Welcome Email
    #end Registration Complete
